data.description:
Lots of love has poured into this charming 3 bed, 2 bath townhouse. Extensively renovated and is the definition of MOVE-IN-READY! Come take notice of the character seen in the new wood floors, new paint in living room and kitchen, recessed lighting, new tile floor, new kitchen cabinets, granite counters, stainless appliances, new sink and backlash in kitchen, master bedroom and full bath, as well as new carpet through out the house + bedrooms. Very spacious & cozy townhome with 2 fireplaces; one in living area, as well as in master bedroom. Come check out the 2 community pools and 2 carport spaces that this place has to offer!
Refrigerator, washer, dryer and all remaining accessories stay.
